This software is designed for educational purposes to assist educators in 
automating grading and assessment tasks. Users are responsible for:

1. Ensuring compliance with their institution's academic integrity policies
2. Properly reviewing and validating AI-generated feedback and grades
3. Maintaining student privacy and data security standards
4. Following applicable educational technology regulations (FERPA, etc.)

The authors and contributors assume no responsibility for misuse of this 
software in educational settings.
